title: Hillary Clinton blasts Benghazi panel as 'partisan arm of the Republican National Committee'
text: Days before she is to testify before of a House panel investigating the Benghazi terrorist attacks, former Secretary of State Hillary Rodham Clinton on Sunday blasted the committee and called it nothing more than a " partisan arm of the Republican National Committee.
